mpox Vaccination by county

Draft Analysis

Data publicly available through MDHHS and CDC.

Data pulled on 4/24/2023

This analysis uses similar methodology to the CDC MMWR JYNNEOS Vaccination Coverage Among Persons at Risk for Mpox — United States, May 22, 2022–January 31, 2023

The larger the color block, the larger the at risk population

The actual color indicates the percentage of first dose vaccinations in the at-risk population (first dose vaccines / total at risk population). The darker the color, the more population that has been vaccinated.
